@plane z=0 label="01 — Planet Telex"
## 01 · Planet Telex
**Timecode IN:** `00:00:00:00`  **Timecode OUT:** `00:04:39:12`

| # | TC | Cue Name | Fixture Group | Action |
|---|-----|----------|---------------|--------|
| Q1.0 | 00:00 | Pre-set | All wash | Full deep blue 204/0/255, 0% dimmer → 35% over 4s |
| Q1.1 | 00:04 | Downbeat | Robe BMFL grid | Snap pan/tilt to audience wash position; iris 60% |
| Q1.2 | 00:08 | Verse 1 | GLP X4 Bar cyc | Slow cyan chase, 0.4 Hz, 100% intensity |
| Q1.3 | 01:12 | Chorus | Full rig | Bump to white 255/255/255; strobe @4Hz for 2 beats then release |
| Q1.4 | 03:58 | Outro swell | Robe BMFL | Fan-out upstage; 8-second iris close to 0% |
| Q1.5 | 04:39 | Blackout | All | Hard blackout snap |

**Haze:** medium continuous from downbeat.  
**Follow-spots:** FOH spot A on Thom from Q1.1; no spot B this song.  
> *Note from Jonny's tech: Jonny's side floor pocket has a practical blue neon — do NOT hit it with strobe.*

@plane z=1 label="02 — The Bends"
## 02 · The Bends
**Timecode IN:** `00:05:10:00`  **Timecode OUT:** `00:08:44:06`

| # | TC | Cue Name | Fixture Group | Action |
|---|-----|----------|---------------|--------|
| Q2.0 | 00:00 | Intro guitar | Robe BMFL USL+USR | Tight spot pools on Colin and Jonny; amber 255/120/0 |
| Q2.1 | 00:22 | Verse 1 | GLP bars | Red pulse on snare hits; program MIDI trigger ch12 |
| Q2.2 | 01:04 | "I wish I was special" | FOH Robe grid | Slow pan sweep 30s, 180° arc, blue→violet fade |
| Q2.3 | 01:52 | Chorus | Full rig | All on, desaturated white; gobo rotation medium |
| Q2.4 | 02:45 | Guitar solo | Robe BMFL DS pair | Tight elliptical wash on Thom DSC; magenta 255/0/140 |
| Q2.5 | 03:30 | Final chorus | Robe all | Swap to harsh white + 1Hz strobe bursts on chord hits |
| Q2.6 | 08:44 | End | All | 6-second fade to blackout |

**Haze:** heavy during chorus. Bump haze off 30s before end.  
**Follow-spots:** Both FOH on Thom from Q2.2. Balcony spot on Phil from Q2.3.  
> Thom goes to piano at Q2.2 — tell spot A operator: TIGHTEN iris to 50%, follow left.

